.hero-unit
  %h1
    Do good with your data
  %p
    Personal data is a valuable commodity.&nbsp;
    It captures the thoughts and sentiments of consumers, and lets advertisers develop highly targeted marketing campaigns.&nbsp;
    Now you can contribute this data to qualified research groups to help them advance their work.&nbsp;
    DataDonor selects the groups that are eligible for the program; you select the data that you wish to upload and share.&nbsp;
    To get started, sign up for an account below.&nbsp; 
    Be a DataDonor today!
    %br/
  %br/
  .btn-toolbar
    .btn-group
      =link_to 'Sign Up', new_user_registration_path, :class=>'btn btn-primary btn-large'
    .btn-group
      = link_to 'Learn More', page_path('about'), :class=>'btn btn-large'